<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<chapter xml:id="ch-determinants" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Determinants</title>

<introduction>
<p>
  Learning goals:
  <ul>
    <li>
      <p>Be able to compute determinants of small matrices using cofactor
		expansion</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>Be familiar with the properties of determinants</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>Be able to compute determinants of larger matrices using properties of determinants</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>Be able to compute determinants of larger matrices using cofactor expansion through
		specific choice of row or column</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>Know the relationship between determinants and inverses</p>
    </li>
  </ul>
</p>  
</introduction>

<xi:include href="sec-4.1-the-cofactor-expansion.ptx" />
<xi:include href="sec-4.2-determinants-and-matrix-inverses.ptx"/>

